BEGIN TRANSACTION;
CREATE TABLE attachments (
  id INTEGER ,
  supplier_id INTEGER DEFAULT 0 ,
  product_id INTEGER DEFAULT 0 ,
  certification_id INTEGER DEFAULT 0 ,

  attachment_filename VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT "",
  attachment_type VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT "",
  attachment_data BLOB DEFAULT "",

  PRIMARY KEY(id ASC)
);
CREATE TABLE categories (
  id INTEGER ,
  name VARCHAR(255) ,
  PRIMARY KEY(id ASC)
);

	"pricing_payment_terms"	TEXT,
	"production_stock"	INTEGER,
	"production_daily_capacity"	INTEGER,
	"production_minimum_order"	INTEGER
);
